  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, in the second session, AI-Assisted Code Refiners had significantly higher scores compared to AI-Reliant Code Generator & Refiners.",
    "These results align with previous studies that emphasize the benefits of active engagement and critical thinking in AI-supported learning environments (Yilmaz & Yilmaz, 2023b).",
    "Students who use AI tools to refine and improve their code, rather than relying on AI just for code generation, appear to develop a deeper understanding and mastery of the programming concepts.",
    "Another study conducted by Pesovski et al. (2024) indicated that high performing students were more reluctant to use AI-generated content to complete their tasks comparing to low performers.",
    "This can also be interpreted as high performing students might not prefer to primarily rely on AI but to engage with task by themselves at first."
  ],
